      "cookedHtml": "<p>Im testing new file column crossboard automations, working fine!<br />\nBut… seeing that if i create a workdoc (for example a template checklist), it doesnt go with another files to the destination board.<br />\nThis is needed in order to have the same files in both boards including workdocs!!!</p>\n<p>In addition, as a bug, when there is a workdoc created, the automation wont move any other file to the destination board, if you remove it and execute the automatization, it works again… this needs to be fixed…</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/f/fbf71337893bcfc33d326bb5ce5076137ee20073.png\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/f/fbf71337893bcfc33d326bb5ce5076137ee20073_2_690x60.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"60\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1088×96 14.4 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/b/b25ac2b1006b11e791622b11c6c0c1846053b782.png\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/b/b25ac2b1006b11e791622b11c6c0c1846053b782_2_488x500.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"488\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">537×550 25 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>BOARD ORIGIN<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/d/d6236880dc2a60f307581dd65138004bf9c14a80.png\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/d/d6236880dc2a60f307581dd65138004bf9c14a80_2_690x19.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"19\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1233×35 4.7 KB</span>